{"tid":1592663,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[名正則言順] 宣傳用詞要正確，「停止綁架」「釋放肉參」","createTime":"2019-09-24T17:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T16:48:18.000Z","uid":178320,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0de5b6709b9154d6f31afc32d1a460ae170c777b","tid":1592663,"uid":178320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:10:27.000Z","msg":"街坊圍住叫黑社會過街老鼠係唔夠架，咩「阿sir madam」佢地更加唔配被尊稱，<br />\n要叫「共匪」「停止綁架市民」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如2015年，李波係被非法匪幫綁架，唔係咩「跨境執法」，話「執法」即係承認佢有權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n唔係咩「犯」，仲有任何「肉參」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />被定罪前都係無罪，只係被告同嫌疑人。<br />\n<br />\n仲有我地可以學泡菜逆權三部曲，見面就嗌簡短版「滅共」或長版「全黨死清光」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地係反中共，不是反中華。<br />\n<br />\nPS. 文宣嚴重受北方口語入侵，應該要用書面語，例如：<br />\n昨日今日明日、一日兩日一百日、冰封三尺非一日之寒、一日不見如隔三秋、明日復明日明日何其多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n昨天今天明天、一天兩天一百天、冰封三尺非一天之寒、一天不見如隔三秋、明天復明天明天何其多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e71e498c81f964ec540d5e27222fac0b0441fa9","tid":1592663,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"15382ab94f5d8e16b31e58b942fa31669876846f","tid":1592663,"uid":261530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:11:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff23a2ec414ed42faa93dbd4babe2418156c0d70","tid":1592663,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:13:16.000Z","msg":"[突發]930三罷 文宣工作立即開始!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https: